                </div>
                <a href="https://www.sodexo.fr/titres-restaurant/" class="d-block my-3" onmouseover="this.style.color='#8282dc'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#55547d'" tabindex="-1" style="color: rgb(85, 84, 125);"> Découvrir les solutions restauration                                </a>
